  "What is the surface area-to-volume ratio, and why does it limit cell size?": "地表面积与体积的比率是多少,为什么限制细胞大小?",
  "Surface area-to-volume ratio and cell size: (1) Mathematical basis: for a sphere, SA = 4πr², V = (4/3)πr³. As r doubles: SA increases 4×, V increases 8× → SA:V ratio halves. For a cube: side length s → SA = 6s², V = s³ → SA:V = 6/s. (2) Biological implications: all exchange between cell and environment (nutrients in, waste out, O₂/CO₂ exchange) occurs across the plasma membrane (surface area). All metabolic activity produces waste and consumes nutrients proportional to volume. When volume grows faster than surface area, the membrane cannot service the cell's metabolic needs → diffusion distances become too great. (3) Solutions organisms use: remain small (bacteria ~1-10 μm, typical animal cell ~10-30 μm). Folded membranes increase effective surface area (microvilli in intestinal cells increase absorptive surface ~20×, mitochondrial cristae). Flattened or elongated shapes (red blood cells are biconcave discs). Multinucleate cells (skeletal muscle fibers). (4) Exceptions: ostrich egg (~15 cm) but metabolically inactive yolk; neurons are long but thin; Caulerpa (giant single-celled alga) uses cytoplasmic streaming.": "表面- 体积比例和细胞大小:(1) 数学基础: 球体: SA = 4 r2, V = 4 r2, V = 4 3 r3 3 。 正正值: SA 增加 4x, V 增加 8x = SA: V = 5 = 6s2, V = s3 SA: V = 6/ s. SA: V = 6/ s. (2) 生物影响: 细胞和环境之间的所有交换(血浆中营养素、废物、 O2/ CO2 交换)发生在血浆中(表层区域) 所有代谢活动产生废物,消耗营养素量与体积成成比例。 当体积比表区域增长更快时, 膜无法满足细胞的代谢需要 = 扩散距离太远。 (3) 溶液生物使用: 仍然很小(细菌 ~ 1- 10 微克, 典型动物细胞细胞 ~ 10 30 mmmmmmmum) ; 红膜- 增加表面积面积(肠细胞细胞 增加吸收细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞 ; 20x; 红树状 ) (红铁 磨 或红 磨 磨 ) (层- 磨) 磨 。",
  "A pathologist examines a tumor biopsy using both light microscopy and TEM, observing cells with enlarged nuclei, abnormal chromatin patterns, increased mitotic figures, and disorganized ultrastructure. Rudolf Virchow, who founded cellular pathology, proposed that disease arises from abnormal cells. How does this case illustrate Virchow's cellular pathology and its connection to cell theory?": "一位病理学家利用光显微镜和 TEM , 观察细胞,观察细胞的核素放大、异常的染色素模式、增加的线性数字和无组织的超结构,对肿瘤进行生物诊断。 创建细胞病理学的鲁道夫·维肖(Rudolf Virchow)提出,疾病源于异常细胞。 这个案例如何说明维肖的细胞病理及其与细胞理论的联系?",
  "Virchow's cellular pathology and cancer: (1) Virchow's 'Die Cellularpathologie' (1858): groundbreaking work proposing that all diseases involve changes in normal cells. Replaced the humoral theory (disease from imbalances in blood, phlegm, yellow bile, black bile) and miasma theory (disease from bad air). Key principle: every pathological condition can be traced to abnormal cellular activity. (2) Cancer connection: Virchow recognized cancer as uncontrolled cell proliferation — tumor cells are derived from normal cells (tenet 3: cells from cells) that have undergone transformation. Modern understanding: cancer results from accumulated mutations in oncogenes (gain-of-function) and tumor suppressors (loss-of-function). (3) Microscopic observations in the biopsy: Enlarged nuclei → genomic instability, aneuploidy. Abnormal chromatin → epigenetic dysregulation, aberrant gene expression. Increased mitotic figures → loss of cell cycle checkpoint control (p53, Rb mutations). Disorganized ultrastructure (TEM) → disrupted organelle organization, abnormal membrane structures. (4) Modern pathology: histopathology (light microscopy of tissue sections) remains the gold standard for cancer diagnosis. EM used for specific tumor classification. Immunohistochemistry and molecular markers complement microscopy. All built on Virchow's foundational insight that disease is cellular.": "Virchow的细胞病理学和癌症:(1) Vircho的细胞病理学和癌症:(1) Vircho的“Die细胞病理学”(1858年):开创性的工作表明所有疾病都涉及正常细胞的变化。取代了幽默理论(与血液、血浆、黄肉、黑肉的不平衡脱节)和Miasma理论(与坏空气脱节脱节)。关键原则:每一种病理病理病理都可追溯到异常细胞活动。(2) 癌症联系:Vircho承认癌症是不受控制的细胞扩散——肿瘤细胞细胞细胞细胞从正常细胞(net3:来自细胞的细胞)中衍生出来。现代理解:在基因(功能上)和肿瘤抑制器(功能损失)中累积的突变的癌症结果。(3) 生物心理学的微观观察:扩大核子基因不稳定、肺炎病病病。正常的染色体分类 — 细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞细胞畸变变的基因表达方式。增加的细胞细胞循环检查控制损失(p53,Rb突变)中的细胞细胞细胞细胞瘤。(4) 机解的细胞基底基根基 用于组织的机械化的系统结构结构(EM)"
